A man, identified as Egwu Francis Emmanuel, has allegedly beaten his wife, Mrs Ezinne to coma in the suburb of Amachara Village, Ebonyi State. According to an eye witness who couldn’t report to the Police for fear of being killed by the culprit who is alleged notoriously known for cult related activities, “This incidence is a repeated occurrence in the neighborhood. Even the wife is afraid to run away from the marriage as she is afraid of what may be her fate. As I’m talking to you now, she is lying in coma in Medical Center Afikpo. . And the husband is still bragging outside of the hospital to pounce on her immediately she regains consciousness. If I see who can have the courage to report this young man to the police, then I would be most grateful. READ ALSO Man rapes, kills brother’s wife in Zamfara He does all these because his immediate elder brother is a Barrister and he brags that nothing can happen to him. So, I am appealing to well meaning Nigerians, especially organizations who fight domestic violence, to come to her rescue.” The couple, who got married December 24th, 2015, is blessed with two children.